OL,3,CCovid inquiry in Belfast: What we
OL,4,Clearned on day one
OL,6,FThe UK's Covid inquiry came to Belfast
OL,7,Fand day one heard explosive claims of
OL,8,Fpolitical in-fighting, lost material
OL,9,Fand disarray within the Northern
OL,10,FIreland Executive as ministers tried
OL,11,Fto deal with the pandemic.
OL,13,FMore than 4,000 people in the region
OL,14,Fdied with the virus across 2020 and
OL,15,F2021.JThe inquiry heard how decision
OL,16,Fmaking came down party-political lines.
